MAKE AN APPOINTMENT TO COME & SEE FOR THIS IS THE PLACE WHERE REFUGE & SERNITIY CAN BE FOUND FROM THE BUSY, NOISY WORLD & A RETREAT, ESCAPE & ENJOYMENT CAN BE EXPERIENCED BY SITTING IN A ROCKING CHAIR ON THE OPEN 10X22 BACK PORCH WATCHING THE SUN RISE IN THE MORNING OR THE MOON SHINING THROUGH THE DARK AT NIGHT WITH ONLY THE SOUNDS OF NATURE RINGING IN YOUR EARS.  THERE IS PLENTY OF SPACE FOR TOYS, VECHICLES, A CAMPERS & RV.   THERE IS ROOM FOR YOUR 4-LEGGED & 2-LEGGED ANIMAL FRIENDS TOO.   PLENTY OF LAND FOR FAMILY GARTHERINGS & TO PLAY ALL SORTS OF GAMES & SPORTS, & THERE IS EVEN A SMALL POND IN THE BACK TO THROW IN A FISHING LINE TO SNAG A FISH OR TWO. THE YARD IS COMPLETELY FENCHED WITH CHAIN LINK FENCING EXCEPT FOR A PIECE THAT IS IN THE FAR BACK OF THE PROPERTY WHERE IT WAS DESIGNED TO BE LEFT RAW FOLIGAE & TIMBER SO AS TO HAVE THE JOY OF EXPERIENCING SETTING UP A TENT & CAMPING ON YOUR OWN WOODED PROPERTY & WITH THE GREAT ADVANTAGE OF IT SERVING AS A PLEASING BUFFER.  -- ENTERING THE FRONT DOOR, YOU ARE SURE TO BE IMPRESSED BY THE SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM WHICH HAS A CEILING FAN & FLOWS SMOOTHLY INTO THE SPLENDID DINING AREA & IT'S EXIT SLIDING GLASS DOORS PROVIDES CHARMING NATURAL LIGHTING TO THIS AREA.   TO THE LEFT OF THE DINING PLACE IS THE SPECTACULAR KITCHEN WITH AN ABUNDANT AMOUNT OF CAPACITY WITH LOADS OF CABINETS & COUNTER SPACE. IT HAS ALSO A CONVENIENT BREAKFAST BAR.  THERE IS A NIFFTY STAINLESS STEEL FARMERS SINK AND A REVERSE OSMOSIS DRINKABLE WATER HOOKED UP TO THE A SMALL FAUCET THAT IS HOOKED UP TO THE ICE MAKER IN THE FRIDGE. THE ENTIRE INTERIOR ROOMS ARE 9 FT TALL WITH ATTRACTIVE CROWN MOLDING EMBELLISHING EACH NOOK AND CRANNY WITHIN THE HOME. ALL 3 BEDROOMS HAVE WALK IN CLOSETS & CECILING FANS.  THE MASTER BEDROOM HAS AN 10'- 8" x 11" 1" BONUS  ROOM THAT OPENS TO A RETREAT OR COULD BE USED AS A COMPUTER ROOM / LIBRARY OR BABY'S NURSERY.  THE MASTER BATHROOM HAS A WALK IN CLOSET & A PANTRY CLOSET & DOUBLE VANITIES.  NUMBER 2 BATHROOM HAS A TUB/WITH SHOWER & DOUBLE VANITIES. THE INSIDE LAUNDRY ROOM IS SUITED WITH ITS OWN EXIT DOOR & THE WASHER & DRYER WILL BE LEFT IN PLACE FOR THE NEW OWNER(S). ALL THE APPLIANCES WILL REMAIN IN THE HOME WHICH INCLUDES 2 FRIGERATORS, FREEZER, RANGE/OVEN, MICROWAVE, DISHWASHER, WATER HEATER & REVERSE OSMOSIS.  SO, BRING YOUR OWN PERSONNAL BELONGINGS & SET UP LIVING IN THE COUNTRY WITH ONLY APPROXIMATELY 22 MILES FROM ST. CLOUD & 30 MILES TO MELBOURNE BEACHES.   OH YES, THERE IS A HANDY NEW METAL GARAGE/ WORKSHOP (23X31) WITH ELECTRICITY & CEMENT FLOORS & ULTIMATE ROOM FOR STORAGE.  THERE ARE TWO WELLS.  ONE THAT IS USED FOR IRRIGATION & THE OTHER IS FOR THE HOUSEHOLD.  THE ONLY WAY TO APPREICATE THIS "GEM " IS TO & MAKE AN APPOINTMNET & COME WITNESS IT'S WORTH.
